{"title_page": "List of video games that support cross-platform play", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n[[Cross-platform play]] is the ability to allow different gaming platforms to share the same online servers in a [[Video game|game]], allowing [[Gamer|players]] to join together regardless of the platform they own. Since the [[Dreamcast]] and [[PlayStation 2]], there have been online video games that support cross-play. Listed here is an incomplete list (which misses some mobile games and Xbox One backwards compatible games) of games that support cross-play with their consoles, computers, mobile and handheld game consoles note when using.\n\n==Games which currently support cross-platform play==\n{{Dynamic list}}\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"width:100%; font-size:86%;\" id=\"softwarelist\"\n|-\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:30%;\"|Title\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:5%;\"|360\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:10%;\"|3DS\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:5%;\"|Linux\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:5%;\"|Mac\n! colspan=\"4\"|Windows PC\n! colspan=\"3\"|Mobile\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:5%;\"|PS3\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:5%;\"|PS4\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:5%;\"|Switch\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:5%;\"|Vita\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:5%;\"|Wii U\n! rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:5%;\"|XBO\n! rowspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\"|{{abbr|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n!{{abbr|GOG|GOG}}\n!{{abbr|Steam|Steam}}\n!{{abbr|W10|Windows 10}}\n!Other\n!{{abbr|iOS|iOS}}\n!{{abbr|Android|Android}}\n!{{abbr|WP|Windows Phone}}\n|-\n| ''#IDARB''\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n| {{yes|W10}}\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n| {{yes|XBO}}\n|\n|-\n| ''[[99Vidas]]''\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|\n| {{yes|PS3}}\n| {{yes|PS4}}\n|\n|\n|\n|\n|align=center|<ref>Sal Romano. [http://gematsu.com/2017/07/beat-em-99vidas-launches-ps4-ps3-ps-vita-july-18-americas Beat 'em up 99Vidas launches for PS4, PS3, and PS Vita on July 18 in the Americas], ''Gematsu'', July 12, 2017.<