ican people of Swedish descent]]\n[[Category:Classical musicians from Massachusetts]]\n[[Category:Decca Records artists]]\n[[Category:Deaths from cancer in Connecticut]]\n[[Category:Easy listening musicians]]\n[[Category:Harvard College alumni]]\n[[Category:Light music composers]]\n[[Category:Musicians from Cambridge, Massachusetts]]\n[[Category:People from Woodbury, Connecticut]]\n[[Category:Pupils of Walter Piston]]\n[[Category:Writers from Cambridge, Massachusetts]]\n", "name_user": "Rolf.Anderson", "label": "safe", "comment": "Bibliography - Periodicals ... added New York Times article; External links ... small adjustment", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leroy_Anderson"}
